Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:10.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.28,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,750)}The Wizard King Saw, Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:03.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey words can't make anything happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:06.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:11.66,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing to fly freely across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:14.00,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed it all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:17.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step I go, though \Nit's a doubtful world 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.55,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care how much I fall
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:23.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct is my guide, I never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:29.56,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To faraway future, I burst out running
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:34.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond even the unseen fears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.87,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision I had, so I can be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:45.12,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will write the next page
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.62,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:51.38,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that page from someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:11.06,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,So these are Hage's famous tatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:16.09,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if they'll be to your liking, \NLord Salim, but help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:27.51,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,They're so dry and flaky. I've never had \Nanything that made me so thirsty before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:33.30,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.51,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:41.10,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that you're \Na splendid cook, Miss Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.32,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not all that good, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:47.13,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Please, eat as much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.40,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Klaus, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.84,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:58.24,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Why must a noble such as myself \Neat this unknown thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.61,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this makes me so thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.66,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:09.92,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Both Yuno and Asta sent us money \Nfrom their first pay as Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:13.82,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,And then... We were able to \Nbuy so many tatoes that we can
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:18.20,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,feed the children as much as \Nthey want to eat every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:23.64,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, couldn't you feed us \Nsomething besides tatoes, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:30.57,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be picky! Look how big \NYuno got from eating tatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:36.02,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, it's wonderful that you're sending \Nmoney home when you're just a newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:37.99,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:40.97,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:45.37,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,You've helped us out a lot.\NAnd not just with the tatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.47,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to plug up \Nthat hole in the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.20,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,We even dug up a well in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.94,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.17,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.96,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's been sending money, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:02.21,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. To think he'd be able to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.50,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,How much is Asta sending?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.99,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.44,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Whisper, whisper, whisper...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.86,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Starting next month,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.14,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send all of my pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:26.28,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Really, you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:30.36,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine for a while \Nwith the amount you sent us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:31.58,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:37.71,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.54,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Salim, we should be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:46.20,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it won't hurt to stay a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:51.73,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,In the future, it'll be important for nobles\Nto have more knowledge of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:56.24,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Lily, may I have some more water?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.75,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:03.63,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's empty. I'll go get some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.76,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:08.01,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. You relax, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.94,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.61,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,It's chilly at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.97,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.61,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:29.16,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing. My body \Njust acted on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.35,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,It's just proper etiquette for a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:52.83,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.38,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.02,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.67,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That brooch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:07.32,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same one the men who were \Nafter Lord Salim were wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.79,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,H-How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:14.21,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! It must be because \NI put my robe on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:17.88,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Lily was taken instead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.36,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:28.29,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sister going to be okay? Is she, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:29.89,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:35.16,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll go save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.39,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.32,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.65,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.00,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.21,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I need all of you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.53,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.07,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:54.31,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission is to escort Lord Salim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.56,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when the enemy \Nwill come after him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.89,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We must leave at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.84,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.29,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,But Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.35,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Four-eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:06.81,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling "Four-eyes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:12.04,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Four... Er, Klaus, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.57,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of this, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:17.17,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, I'm sure you're \Nworried about the sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:20.30,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,but let's leave her to the authorities \Nwho have jurisdiction here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:21.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.85,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go, Lord Salim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:26.20,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:29.33,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.55,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.61,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:33.89,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.02,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We must fulfill our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.81,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Disobeying an order is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'm going to go save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.81,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:49.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:04.95,main,Meha,0000,0000,0000,,You're confusing recklessness \Nwith courage, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:06.75,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.26,main,Meha,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.55,main,Meha,0000,0000,0000,,Meha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.59,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Towering Tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.39,main,Meha,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:22.98,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,One down,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.69,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,four to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.61,main,Miha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to kill you or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.21,main,Miha,0000,0000,0000,,but I've got to at least \Nrough you up a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:44.52,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you were after me all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:48.60,main,Miha,0000,0000,0000,,You're brighter than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.39,main,Miha,0000,0000,0000,,Can't breathe, eh? Then drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.50,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,How is this magic supposed to drown me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.59,main,Miha,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.61,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This is how
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.65,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,you're supposed to drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.57,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:45.35,main,Muha,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you completely \Nfell for the footsteps I laid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.59,main,Muha,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, and that, and that, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.86,main,Muha,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad. In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:59.16,main,Muha,0000,0000,0000,,There! Think you can stop that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.01,main,Muha,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.37,main,Muha,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:12.38,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Why is size the only thing \Nthat matters to you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.62,main,Muha,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:22.07,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's three. Two more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.64,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.27,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.44,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.41,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a shame
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:47.75,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,if the sister's pretty face got burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.85,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:12.40,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you have a talent for magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:17.65,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,If you see someone in need, \Nmake sure you help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.32,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:21.55,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.39,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:33.79,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Yuno. Why don't \Nyou hand over your grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:37.51,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to do anything without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.26,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with my grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:44.65,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll sell it. Maybe I'll burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:47.26,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:52.27,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,Without your grimoire,\Nyou'll be useless as a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.06,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.65,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.18,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.94,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good boy. Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:11.93,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll let you take \Nyour precious sister home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.60,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.36,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Don't you get it? The sister—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.35,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you harm her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:25.23,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to attack me? \NNo matter how you attack—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:26.94,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who's going to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.01,main,Maha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then who—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:33.01,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Creation Magic: Fierce Spiral Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.24,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.34,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.07,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,She's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.57,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you defeated all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.83,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,There should be one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.25,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Did he flee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.27,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What would you have done if I hadn't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:04.18,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.46,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm some kind of fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.56,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He does!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:17.43,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, Yuno. Our duty as Magic \NKnights is to protect the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:27.78,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,These men were after you, not Salim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.08,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think a noble would want \Nto come to a village like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:35.85,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they'd happily eat those tatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:39.71,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to say it, but I definitely wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:44.28,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they'd accidentally take \NSister Lily instead of Salim, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.26,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:50.10,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It was strange for Salim, whom you defeated, \Nto specifically ask you to escort him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:56.60,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when we used my Plant \NCreation Magic: Flower of Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:02.15,flashback,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault I wasn't able \Nto join the Magic Knights, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:07.74,flashback,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about your stupid four-leaf \Ngrimoire, damn it?! I'll steal it from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:11.45,flashback,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my daddy to hurt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.25,flashback,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.85,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He coughed up everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:20.63,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still surprised you managed to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.92,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That was also thanks to Mimosa's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:27.85,flashback,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Flower Creation Magic: \NMagic Flower Guidepost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.72,flashback,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:33.29,flashback,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:37.91,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we were able to back you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.80,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:46.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me out a lot, Klaus, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:48.85,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.23,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.70,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, revenge? How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.62,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural that you lost to Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:05.67,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Our honorable captain of the Golden Dawn, \NWilliam Vangeance, chose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:09.23,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That means he's truly that talented!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:11.59,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.20,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:21.35,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't acknowledged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.69,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.94,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:31.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll overlook your insolence this time, \Nsince this was all Salim's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.70,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,So what shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Take him to the royal capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.90,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's just leave them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.46,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.21,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they don't go \Nnear Hage Village again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:58.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him. You're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.60,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever try anything like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.32,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:06.17,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.41,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Getting you to let your guard \Ndown was all part of my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:11.68,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:14.15,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,God of Lighting Rising Salim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:15.57,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Holy Strike of Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:22.65,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this! Show some remorse \Nfor what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.20,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.46,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.86,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I almost want to scout the \Nsister for the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:36.34,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, we're going to take them \Nto the royal capital after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:41.20,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where did the other one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.48,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:53.53,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:59.86,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,If they were actually in trouble, I was \Ngoing save them, but I didn't need to at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:04.33,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,William's newbie is pretty impressive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.77,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend to fool around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.28,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:14.13,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,You need to return at once! \NYour work is piling up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.21,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:18.56,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's not healthy to be so \Nirritated all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.81,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think that is, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:26.27,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.48,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.57,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.41,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome as usual, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:32.32,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he is a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:37.17,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus, Mimosa, thank you both very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.51,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:44.34,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Salim was behind all of this. How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:49.44,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please, help yourselves.\NLet me repay you with more tato dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:53.08,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,They've gotten a bit cold,\Nbut please eat as much as you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.67,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.42,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not very honest, are you, Klaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:22.87,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.80,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:39.14,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King was pleased with \Nyour work, and we received a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:42.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much! It's an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:47.13,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd get \None on my first mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:52.02,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't feel as if we did \Nenough to earn a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.96,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,After you brought Salim in, \Nhe ended up confessing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:19:00.37,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,to various evil deeds Lord Hapshass had done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:04.21,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Bribes, fraudulent accounts, \Nand shady deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.08,main,Willaim,0000,0000,0000,,You made quite the catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.17,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:13.80,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, did you happen to take on this mission \Nbecause you knew this would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:20.18,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't allow any evil deeds \Nto be done in the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.55,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:29.62,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus, Yuno, and Mimosa, I look forward \Nto all of your future great deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.31,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.62,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno and Mimosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:39.22,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the newbies this year are... \Nwell, at least slightly competent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:50.55,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you all. \NEspecially you, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.89,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,So, a star...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:20:02.39,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Everything ended well this time, but don't \Never act on your own again, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:08.53,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Why was there a pause? Yuno, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.91,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Look me in the eyes and say that \Nyou won't act on your own again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:12.88,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:15.22,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! Hey, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:23.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The Golden Dawn received a star?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.57,main,Doll,0000,0000,0000,,We are hoomans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:31.70,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought we were finally only \N100 away. Now we're 101 away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I thought we'd \Nfinally caught up to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:44.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How is that close? We're at minus 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.20,main,Doll,0000,0000,0000,,We are hoomans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:49.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:53.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They're only ahead by 101! \NI'll catch up in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:59.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:14.07,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, there's trouble. An anomaly—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.72,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,An anomaly has occurred, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:23.39,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Let's have them work on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:24.77,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:42.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:49.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again in the small closed off classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:57.62,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The star of the class was shining yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:22:03.98,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They shine so bright that I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:07.51,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.22,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That the revolution was within my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:18.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange? If you want \Nto laugh, go ahead and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:25.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us who were left \Nbehind wanted to become something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:32.93,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We repeat the same morning over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:39.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who \Ncan choose your tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:44.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beyond our current selves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:03.36,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:02.92,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:06.86,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(522,1)}My Steed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.91,0:23:05.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,"My Steed."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:14.21,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't it beautiful? Its eyes,\Nits beak... Perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:15.54,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.23,0:23:19.51,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it just scream "Golden Dawn"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:20.64,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:24.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's so cool! What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:29.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's as cool as Magna's Crazy Cyclone\N and Bah-ha's Shooting Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:33.51,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? I have no idea \Nwho you are, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.36,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:41.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What? Explore a dungeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:44.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Stupidsta and Luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:47.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me. Exploring \Na dungeon will be easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:51.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 14: "Dungeon."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:55.50,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 14\N\N{\fs18}Dungeon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:53.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic.
